# 🌿 Yasho Natural Products - E-Commerce Website (Docker + AWS)

A modern **static e-commerce website** for natural and organic products built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Docker, and AWS EC2**.

This project demonstrates how to deploy a website using **Docker and Nginx on a cloud server**.

create directory 
  
1. website2/
└── index.html


  
2. Install Docker
sudo apt update
sudo apt install docker.io -y
sudo systemctl start docker
sudo systemctl enable docker
  
3. Run the website using Docker
docker run -d -p 8080:80 \
  -v $(pwd):/usr/share/nginx/html \
  --name yashoshop nginx
  
4. Open in browser
publicip:8080

Make sure to open this port in Security Group:
inbond rules
Type	Port	Source
Custom TCP	8080	0.0.0.0/0


Web servers like Nginx automatically load index.html as the default homepage.
Without it, the website will not open correctly.
